            <h3 class="resource-card__title">Kotlin</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="resource-card__desc">
            JetBrains' Kotlin documentation is well-organized and includes comparisons with Java, making it accessible to
            existing JVM developers. Covers Android development, multiplatform projects, and coroutines in depth.
          </p>
