            efficiently.
          </p>
          <div class="resource-card__links">
            <a href="<https://svelte.dev/docs>" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-link resource-link--primary">Svelte Documentation</a>
            <a href="<https://learn.svelte.dev/>" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-link">Interactive Tutorial</a>
            <a href="<https://kit.svelte.dev/docs>" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-link">SvelteKit</a>
