            <a href="<https://start.solidjs.com/>" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-link">SolidStart</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Tailwind CSS -->
        <article class="resource-card" data-search="tailwind tailwindcss utility first css framework responsive design">
          <div class="resource-card__header">
            <h3 class="resource-card__title">Tailwind CSS</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="resource-card__desc">
            Tailwind's utility-first CSS framework documentation is comprehensive and searchable. Covers all utility classes,
